OL,3,CTwo men arrested in connection with
OL,4,CGolders Green arson attack
OL,6,FTwo men aged 47 and 45 have been
OL,7,Farrested in connection with the
OL,8,FGolders Green arson attack, the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,11,FCounter-terrorism police are leading
OL,12,Fthe investigation into the attack on
OL,13,Ffour ambulances belonging to a Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunity charity in North London.
OL,16,FMonday's incident is being treated as
OL,17,Fan antisemitic hate crime by the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police and has not been
OL,19,Fdeclared a terrorist incident, the
OL,20,Fforce said.
