OL,3,CTwo men arrested in connection with
OL,4,CGolders Green arson attack
OL,6,FPolice have since set up an online
OL,7,Fportal for members of the public to
OL,8,Fshare any video footage they have
OL,9,Fbefore, during, or after the incident.
OL,11,FThere were no injuries reported in the
OL,12,Fattack on the Jewish-led ambulance
OL,13,Fservice, Hatzola.
OL,15,FMultiple cylinders on the vehicles had
OL,16,Fexploded during the fire, causing
OL,17,Fwindows to break in an adjacent block
OL,18,Fof flats.
