OL,6,FHatzola is a non-profit, volunteer
OL,7,Forganisation that provides hospital
OL,8,Ftransportation and emergency care to
OL,9,Fthe local community, regardless of
OL,10,Freligion.
OL,12,FThis is a breaking news story, more to
OL,13,Ffollow
